Pasadena Refining Has Foaming in Cooling Tower at Texas Plant

-- B y   L e e l a   L a n d r e s s
-- 
2011-02-14T15:56:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-14/pasadena-refining-has-foaming-in-cooling-tower-at-texas-plant.html
Pasadena Refining System Inc., a
unit of  Petroleo Brasileiro SA , had foaming in one of the
cooling towers at its refinery in  Pasadena ,  Texas , according to
a message left on a community hot line.  To contact the reporter on this story:
